### Get le feed de discussions d'une action
GET {{api}}/rest/v1/action_discussion_feed?action_id=eq.eci_1.1
apikey: {{anon}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Upsert une discussion - Premier commentaire
POST {{api}}/rest/v1/action_discussion_feed
apikey: {{anon}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
prefer: return=representation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collectivite_id": 1,
  "action_id": "eci_1.1",
  "status": "ouvert",
  "commentaires": [
    {
      "message": "yolo"
    }
  ]
}

